  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Users can create customer label pages for price sheets, label printing, and more. Printing a list of items can be helpful to your staff, such as reference sheets for common sale items/services to scan at checkout and inventory scan lists for items that don't have their own labels.</p><h3 id=\"PrintaCatalogItemReferenceSheet-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932427464/Inventory+Count+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932427464\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Inventory Count Process: Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1931018355/The+RepairQ+Catalog\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1931018355\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Catalog Overview</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932525576/RepairQ+Best+Practices+-+Inventory+Management+101\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932525576\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RepairQ Best Practices - Inventory Management 101</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932361762/RepairQ+Best+Practices+-+Inventory+Management+102\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932361762\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RepairQ Best Practices - Inventory Management 102</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"PrintaCatalogItemReferenceSheet-PrintingaCatalogItemListSheet\">Printing a Catalog Item List Sheet</h2><p /><p>1. On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Settings</strong> \u2192 <strong>Location Settings</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Label%20Reference%20Sheet%201.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. On the Settings Overview page, click <strong>Catalog</strong> from the list of options on the left column. From the dropdown, click <strong>Print Label Pages</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"226\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Label%20Reference%20Sheet%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. Use the filters to customize your page settings, display information, and catalog items on your list.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Label%20Reference%20Sheet%203.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><strong>Page Title</strong> - Create a title for the page.</p></li><li><p><strong>Columns/Rows</strong> - This controls the number of rows and columns per page. By default, the sheet will print in two columns with four rows on each page.</p></li><li><p><strong>Page Numbers</strong> - Select this option to include the page number on the label page.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Label%20Reference%20Sheet%204.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><strong>Display Settings</strong> - Select what catalog item details will be included on the page.</p></li><li><p><strong>Barcode Format</strong> - If opting to print a barcode, select the format. The most common format is Code39.</p></li><li><p><strong>Barcode Size</strong> - If printing a barcode, select the height, in pixels.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Label%20Reference%20Sheet%205.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><strong>Item Type</strong> - Filter results by a specific item type.</p></li><li><p><strong>Manufacturer</strong> - Filter results by a specific manufacturer.</p></li><li><p><strong>Catalog Item</strong> - Filter for results that include a specific keyword.</p></li><li><p><strong>Filter Focus</strong> - Select whether the list will include inventoried items, serialized items, and if the list will include inactive catalog items.</p></li></ul><p /><p>4. After you have made your selections, click <strong>Apply Filters</strong>. Your list will show as a preview below the filter section.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Label%20Reference%20Sheet%206.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Label%20Reference%20Sheet%207.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>5. Click the <strong>Print button</strong> at the top-right of the screen to print the page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933344820/Label%20Reference%20Sheet%208.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
